metadata.name: Scene 1 Air Delivery
metadata.description: Buzz with Dank (BWD) docnifty is a fun 30-minute doc for adults and chronicles the life of an ole stoner and his best bud. BWD NFTs grant access to member only areas, benefits, and perks. This 32 NFT video collection consists of 30 scenes and 2 trailers and lives on the Ethereum blockchain. The scenes are numbered in chronological order of how the docnifty should be viewed. Each NFT can stand alone but tell the entire story as a cohesive collection. These NFTs are sold separately and not as one complete set to make it interesting to acquire the entire collection. The distribution is limited to one of each to make it rare. This collection kickstarts the Buzz with Dank adventure project, and the owners of the BWD docnifty NFTs will receive extra perks, plus the benefits from the BWD 10k collection. For more info, go to BuzzWithDank.com.
